---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="A little about Keaton Wall and this site.">
  <article class="wrap prose">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Keaton. I write here about the things I'm learning and building,
      mostly so I actually remember them, and because every so often someone
      else is stuck on the same thing I just worked through.
    </p>
    <p>
      A few different things show up here and they don't always overlap. The
      technical work of building software and systems. Ideas I'm still chewing
      on. Lessons from work and leadership, which usually show up the hard way.
      And the parts of life that give the rest its meaning (faith, family, and
      everything around them).
    </p>
    <p>
      That's a wide range on purpose. This is a personal site, not a niche.
      If something here is useful to you, that's a bonus. Mostly I'm writing
      to think.
    </p>
    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/keatonwall">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="/rss.xml">Subscribe via RSS</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
